column5: Sorry I lost contact for a bit and have a new account now on the site. I had a few guys ask me some questions about Twin Lakes Outfitters Kag Lake and I lost there names and questions. If you were one of them please PM me again under this name and I'll reply asap.
Hi Mike, good to see your still kicking and offering up info
Mike is the Yoda of outpost fishing in northern Ontario, can't think of anybody that has more hands on experience in my area.
I've been very lucky with fishing and hunting in the area and its one of my favorite parts of Ontario. Only problem is its so far away that I can't fish it more often.

Thanks Phil and are you still making the trip up year and how about Rice have you fished it in the last couple years. With the new slot limits on Rice a few years back the walleye population has real grown and fishing improved.
